    mc "¡Indique el camino!"

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/sy/sm1cs-sy002i.rpy:27
translate spanish sm1cs_sy002i_first_time_f1ad6678:

    # mc "You know, this place is going to be amazing once it's done. But..."
    mc "Sabes, este lugar va a ser increíble una vez que esté terminado. Pero..."

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/sy/sm1cs-sy002i.rpy:28
translate spanish sm1cs_sy002i_first_time_fb6459f9:

    # mc "I wish we could film something right now. Could definitely use the money to help pay for the renovation."
    mc "Ojalá pudiéramos filmar algo en este momento. Definitivamente podría utilizar el dinero para ayudar a pagar la renovación."

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/sy/sm1cs-sy002i.rpy:30
translate spanish sm1cs_sy002i_first_time_4de0426e:

    # sy "Yeah, I know. All the dust and paint doesn't scream 'high quality porn'."
    sy "Sí, lo sé. Todo el polvo y la pintura no gritan 'porno de alta calidad'."

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/sy/sm1cs-sy002i.rpy:34
translate spanish sm1cs_sy002i_first_time_6fbfd622:

    # sy "Which is why we need to get creative."
    sy "Por eso necesitamos ser creativo."

# game/code/scenes/character_scenes/sy/sm1cs-sy002i.rpy:36
translate spanish sm1cs_sy002i_first_time_e7baa3c7:

